{"id":273,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":273,"title":"Revelation 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","John also sees in the sixth seal the Restoration of the gospel, the sealing of the 144,000, and the hosts of the exalted from all nations."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.1","order":"03.29.007.27577"},["b","1"],"And after these things I saw four",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"angels"],"standing on the four corners of the earth, holding the four",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"winds"],"of the earth, that the wind should not blow on the earth, nor on the sea, nor on any tree."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.2","order":"03.29.007.27578"},["b","2"],"And I saw another angel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"ascending"],"from the east, having the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"seal"],"of the living God: and he cried with a loud voice to the four angels, to whom it was given to hurt the earth and the sea,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.3","order":"03.29.007.27579"},["b","3"],"Saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Hurt"],"not the earth, neither the sea, nor the trees, till we have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"sealed"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"servants"],"of our God in their foreheads."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.4","order":"03.29.007.27580"},["b","4"],"And I heard the number of them which were sealed:",["i","and there were"],"sealed an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"hundred"],["i","and"],"forty",["i","and"],"four thousand of all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"tribes"],"of the children of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.5","order":"03.29.007.27581"},["b","5"],"Of the tribe of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Juda"],["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Reuben"],["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Gad",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.6","order":"03.29.007.27582"},["b","6"],"Of the tribe of Aser",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Nepthalim",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Manasses",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.7","order":"03.29.007.27583"},["b","7"],"Of the tribe of Simeon",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Levi",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Issachar",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.8","order":"03.29.007.27584"},["b","8"],"Of the tribe of Zabulon",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Joseph"],["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand. Of the tribe of Benjamin",["i","were"],"sealed twelve thousand."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.9","order":"03.29.007.27585"},["b","9"],"After this I beheld, and, lo, a great multitude, which no man could number, of all nations, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"kindreds"],", and people, and tongues, stood before the throne, and before the Lamb, clothed with white robes, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"palms"],"in their hands;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.10","order":"03.29.007.27586"},["b","10"],"And cried with a loud voice, saying, Salvation to our God which sitteth upon the throne, and unto the Lamb."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.11","order":"03.29.007.27587"},["b","11"],"And all the angels stood round about the throne, and",["i","about"],"the elders and the four",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"beasts"],", and fell before the throne on their faces, and worshipped God,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.12","order":"03.29.007.27588"},["b","12"],"Saying, Amen: Blessing, and glory, and wisdom, and thanksgiving, and honour, and power, and might,",["i","be"],"unto our God for ever and ever. Amen."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.13","order":"03.29.007.27589"},["b","13"],"And one of the elders answered, saying unto me, What are these which are arrayed in white robes? and whence came they?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14","order":"03.29.007.27590"},["b","14"],"And I said unto him, Sir, thou knowest. And he said to me, These are they which came",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"out"],"of great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"tribulation"],", and have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"washed"],"their robes, and made them",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"white"],"in the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"blood"],"of the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_14f"},"Lamb"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.15","order":"03.29.007.27591"},["b","15"],"Therefore are they before the throne of God, and serve him day and night in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"temple"],": and he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sitteth"],"on the throne shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"dwell"],"among them."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.16","order":"03.29.007.27592"},["b","16"],"They shall hunger no more, neither",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"thirst"],"any more; neither shall the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"sun"],"light on them, nor any heat."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.17","order":"03.29.007.27593"},["b","17"],"For the Lamb which is in the midst of the throne shall feed them, and shall lead them unto living fountains of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"waters"],": and God shall wipe away all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"tears"],"from their eyes."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.1a","order":"03.29.007.27594"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.8"},"D&C 77:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.1b","order":"03.29.007.27596"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/37.9"},"Ezek. 37:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.4"},"Dan. 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.2a","order":"03.29.007.27598"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.9"},"D&C 77:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.2b","order":"03.29.007.27600"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seal"},"TG Seal"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.3a","order":"03.29.007.27602"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/9.4"},"Rev. 9:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.3b","order":"03.29.007.27604"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.4.1-5"},"Rev. 22:4 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.3c","order":"03.29.007.27606"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/high-priest-melchizedek-priesthood"},"TG High Priest, Melchizedek Priesthood"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/servant"},"Servant"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.4a","order":"03.29.007.27608"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.11"},"D&C 77:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.4b","order":"03.29.007.27610"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.4c","order":"03.29.007.27612"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.9"},"D&C 77:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.5a","order":"03.29.007.27614"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-judah-people-of"},"TG Israel, Judah, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.5b","order":"03.29.007.27616"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/48.31.6-7,31"},"Ezek. 48:31 (6–7, 31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.8a","order":"03.29.007.27618"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.9a","order":"03.29.007.27620"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.9"},"Rev. 5:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.9b","order":"03.29.007.27622"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18.18-19"},"Ezek. 41:18 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.11a","order":"03.29.007.27624"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14a","order":"03.29.007.27626"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14b","order":"03.29.007.27628"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/tribulation"},"TG Tribulation"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14c","order":"03.29.007.27630"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.19"},"3 Ne. 27:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"TG Purity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wash"},"Wash"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14d","order":"03.29.007.27632"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"14e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14e","order":"03.29.007.27634"},["b","14e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/1.7"},"1 Jn. 1:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"14f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.14f","order":"03.29.007.27636"},["b","14f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lamb-of-god"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lamb of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.15a","order":"03.29.007.27638"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.15b","order":"03.29.007.27640"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/47.8"},"Ps. 47:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.13"},"D&C 88:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.15c","order":"03.29.007.27642"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.16a","order":"03.29.007.27644"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.10"},"Isa. 49:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.16b","order":"03.29.007.27646"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/121.6"},"Ps. 121:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.17a","order":"03.29.007.27648"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/living-water"},"TG Living Water"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.17b","order":"03.29.007.27650"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/21.4"},"Rev. 21:4"],"."]]}
